Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.40,0:00:04.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ahem!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.10,0:00:08.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Y'all want Sensei ta hurry on back, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.54,0:00:10.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.54,0:00:14.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, to welcome him back nice an' proper...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.61,0:00:18.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...let's get this place sparklin' clean!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.08,0:00:19.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.45,0:00:22.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Most of the mess here is because of Miwa-{\i1}chan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.58,0:00:24.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kids? Don't let her fool you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.59,0:00:28.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, get busy and start workin' for Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.39,0:00:30.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.06,0:00:38.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder when Sensei's gonna be back...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.07,0:00:39.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder when...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.41,0:00:47.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.28,0:00:50.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry on home!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.55,0:00:55.45,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,45)}"Should not go to the island"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.12,0:01:00.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.35,0:02:35.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Mother...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.35,0:02:37.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What's this about...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.39,0:02:38.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.99,0:02:42.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...it's my silent protest against your going to the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.42,0:02:44.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Silent?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.09,0:02:48.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I already submitted my work to the exhibit, so I was thinking of going home to the island...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.73,0:02:50.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Going home?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.70,0:02:52.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This {\i1}is{\i0} your home!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.27,0:02:55.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're just a visitor on the island, you ungrateful kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.84,0:02:57.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Mother! Stop...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.21,0:02:58.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No, I won't stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.21,0:03:01.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,"I Won't Stop Until You\NSay You Won't Go" Punch!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.21,0:03:05.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Let's talk first! The punches just plain hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.28,0:03:07.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What are you two doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.52,0:03:09.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kawafuji-{\i1}kun{\i0} is with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.25,0:03:10.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What? Kawafuji-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.95,0:03:13.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kawafuji! You came at the right time!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.22,0:03:17.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I came to say that your work was safely submitted, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.43,0:03:18.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.93,0:03:20.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it's not a bother!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.20,0:03:21.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.20,0:03:22.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go out and grab a bite!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.96,0:03:24.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sei-{\i1}san{\i0}? Are you trying to run?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.93,0:03:29.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I can let this go!\NLet's all think together on this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.14,0:03:31.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Help me convince him, Kawafuji-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.44,0:03:37.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I was against it from the very beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.31,0:03:41.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't do anything back then because the man next to me just went ahead with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.65,0:03:47.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,From what I heard, it seems like you got sick and were even hospitalized.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.12,0:03:50.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I kept an eye on your cat allergies while you were here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.12,0:03:51.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.66,0:03:54.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I told you not to go, you'd go anyways, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.80,0:03:57.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If so, then I'm not going to listen to your opinions!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.73,0:04:00.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stop you, even if it means confining you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.84,0:04:03.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Your mom is quite something...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.84,0:04:06.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So, finally resorting to force...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.47,0:04:10.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well, what your mom is saying makes sense. Just give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.25,0:04:13.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! I thought you were on my side!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.25,0:04:18.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I know you can write calligraphy in Tokyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.09,0:04:22.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...I'd rather have you work yourself silly than lie around on the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.02,0:04:24.33,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,45)}"The Opposition"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.26,0:04:24.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the system?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.43,0:04:31.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, a "remote island" sounds like a place so rural that there's no electricity...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.43,0:04:32.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.77,0:04:37.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That just means it's away from the mainland;\NI can get everything I need to live there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.04,0:04:40.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I was always the reclusive type, so I can get by well enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.71,0:04:45.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have many friends here...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.21,0:04:47.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy enough writing calligraphy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.45,0:04:50.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wow... This is just depressing...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.52,0:04:54.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think the location is all that worries me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.19,0:04:56.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.39,0:05:00.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You've... been hanging around weird people, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.36,0:05:03.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Your attitude and speech have changed for the worse!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.87,0:05:06.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You weren't like that before...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.50,0:05:08.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Am I that bad now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.50,0:05:12.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well, not so much bad. More like weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.81,0:05:14.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Bad company ruins good morals!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.58,0:05:17.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Use judgment in who you associate with!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.25,0:05:19.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Bad company ruins...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.52,0:05:25.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no, no, no, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.85,0:05:27.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, "no"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.19,0:05:29.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You've been acting strange ever since you returned!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.42,0:05:31.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You keep eating pickles for some reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.33,0:05:34.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...and say strange things like "komonno" and "nusano"!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.56,0:05:36.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.00,0:05:37.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not being influenced at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.77,0:05:39.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I think you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.23,0:05:42.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sei-{\i1}san{\i0} never used to raise his voice like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.21,0:05:52.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If it's a matter of location and people,\NI don't see any problems at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.05,0:05:54.42,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,45)}"The Supporters"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.11,0:05:54.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Dad's going to go with this system too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.92,0:05:59.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I used to live on the island back when I was Seishu's age.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.39,0:06:00.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing is wrong with the environment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.96,0:06:03.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You lived on the island too, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.46,0:06:08.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't have forced you to go there if I hadn't gone there myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.06,0:06:10.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kido Yujiro's been taking care of you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.60,0:06:12.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kido...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.90,0:06:13.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Village Leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.94,0:06:15.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.30,0:06:18.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I had some photos in one of my old albums.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.14,0:06:22.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! There's no way I'll let you show something that will help your cause!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.24,0:06:25.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This is just a walk down memory lane.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.65,0:06:27.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Pooh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.78,0:06:30.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.42,0:06:34.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know you kept such old photos.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.22,0:06:37.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Seimei-{\i1}sensei{\i0}, you look just like Handa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.06,0:06:39.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,My eyes aren't as harsh as his.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.49,0:06:42.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Here. It's a photo of me when I was on the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.73,0:06:44.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.33,0:06:46.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa... Village Leader's so young!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.33,0:06:48.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I believe this was 35 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.50,0:06:51.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It was when I went fishing for {\i1}hisanio{\i0} with Kido.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.11,0:06:52.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hisanio{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.17,0:06:54.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,There! "Nusano"!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.31,0:06:56.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We caught a {\i1}hisanio{\i0} too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.48,0:06:58.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well, more like...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.25,0:06:59.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.41,0:07:01.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Is this Kinoshita Shoten?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.25,0:07:03.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I believe that was the name.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.92,0:07:05.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the owner?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.45,0:07:09.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So young! She was good-looking!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.26,0:07:11.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! This river is still there too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.03,0:07:13.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I got hurt there once.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.43,0:07:15.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Me too! I still have the scar here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.36,0:07:17.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I've had enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.43,0:07:22.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You all are only thinking of going to the island!\NNo one understands my feelings!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.47,0:07:24.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you tell I'm really worried?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.87,0:07:27.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're too irresponsible, Da-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.18,0:07:31.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you see our precious son is heading down the path of destruction?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.21,0:07:32.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Da-{\i1}chan{\i0}...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.21,0:07:33.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Now calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.95,0:07:38.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If separation can help a child mature, that is for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.05,0:07:40.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you on my side, Da-{\i1}chan{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.22,0:07:46.73,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,45)}"Mommy" "Mommy" "Mommy"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.89,0:07:47.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're tossing aside your mother, who was there for you through all your sick days?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.40,0:07:49.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Impiety, as vast as the mountains!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.30,0:07:51.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Your mom is really a pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.47,0:07:54.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's how you folks disrespect mothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.74,0:07:56.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,She heard me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.70,0:07:59.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Undutiful, as quick as the winds!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.81,0:08:02.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You all don't know anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.18,0:08:03.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Missus! Ow! Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.91,0:08:06.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Kawafuji-{\i1}kun...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.85,0:08:10.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, I probably can't return for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.02,0:08:12.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Seishu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.39,0:08:15.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I was the one who told you to go to the island, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.19,0:08:17.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...the rest is up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.39,0:08:22.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If you were able to write the calligraphy you wanted to write, you can always come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.73,0:08:24.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's your call from here on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.03,0:08:29.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sei-{\i1}san{\i0} is such a meanie!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.57,0:08:33.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I keep wishing only for the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.68,0:08:40.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The calligraphy for the exhibit is done, and I think I know my way now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.75,0:08:43.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe there's no need for me to rush back to the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.52,0:08:48.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If you're gonna be reclusive no matter where,\NI think it's more convenient to stay in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.06,0:08:54.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much I think,\NTokyo is still better...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.73,0:08:57.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Then why am I this troubled...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.40,0:08:59.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sei-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.07,0:09:03.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This parcel just arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.60,0:09:06.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like it's from the island residents.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.71,0:09:08.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Could it be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.31,0:09:10.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Your belongings, meaning to never come back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.71,0:09:13.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No, they wouldn't do a thing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.48,0:09:15.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I asked them to send me
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.25,0:09:18.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,some documents I needed back when I was under the pressure of the exhibit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.82,0:09:21.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.76,0:09:23.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Those kids...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.26,0:09:25.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,They just threw in anything they could...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.63,0:09:27.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Teasing...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.13,0:09:29.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,My son is being teased...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.13,0:09:31.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.27,0:09:34.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This must be from Naru.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.14,0:09:36.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Who?! Who is Naru?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.17,0:09:37.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,She's a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.01,0:09:40.44,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,42)}"To Sensei
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.01,0:09:40.44,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,76)}I got a gold award. Next up
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.01,0:09:40.44,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(361,107)}is the prefecture's exhibit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.01,0:09:40.44,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,135)}Tama"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.47,0:09:41.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.44,0:09:41.97,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,45)}"I got a silver award
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.44,0:09:41.97,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,73)}Curse Tama"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.91,0:09:45.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,They sent these too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.45,0:09:47.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sei-{\i1}san{\i0}...? What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.62,0:09:50.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's calligraphy written by the kids I'm teaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.45,0:09:52.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.35,0:09:54.79,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(361,45)}"Visiting Old, Learning New
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.35,0:09:54.79,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,76)}Yamamura Miwa, second year, class one"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.35,0:09:55.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty good for only starting recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.99,0:10:02.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If the assignment results were going to come in so soon, I should have left after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.36,0:10:01.63,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,45)}"Visiting Old, Learning New"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.33,0:10:08.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I should have been with them for their results...\NTo congratulate and encourage them...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.27,0:10:09.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sei-{\i1}san...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.61,0:10:16.64,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,45)}"Should not go to the island"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.11,0:10:20.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Do what you please already!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.21,0:10:22.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Mother! Are you pouting again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.28,0:10:24.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not pouting!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.19,0:10:27.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If someone needs you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.66,0:10:30.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...then you have to go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.46,0:10:31.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.83,0:10:35.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But from now on, make sure you call us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.20,0:10:42.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So... does that mean I can go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.30,0:10:44.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.84,0:10:50.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.85,0:10:52.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.41,0:10:56.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,He was thinking of wanting to do something for others.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.15,0:10:59.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Any more from me, and it would have just been me being selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.69,0:11:02.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it wasn't only his calligraphy that matured.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.03,0:11:07.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That island is a wonderful place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.43,0:11:11.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go there before the cold settles in, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.10,0:11:12.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.74,0:11:21.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ahem. Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.78,0:11:26.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We just received word from the village phone keeper, Akki...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.51,0:11:30.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei's gonna be coming home on a plane arriving this evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.05,0:11:31.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.92,0:11:33.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.02,0:11:36.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get this place sparklin' clean for sure this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.09,0:11:38.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.13,0:11:41.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei is going to get really angry if we don't clean up, so let's do our best!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.26,0:11:45.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So heavy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.70,0:11:51.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta hand it to Sensei, coming back to the island just as suddenly as he left...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.27,0:11:54.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,They better be cleaning up the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.98,0:11:59.07,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,42)}"click-click-click"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.99,0:12:18.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe how much time we've wasted...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.13,0:12:19.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.13,0:12:21.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hiro-{\i1}nii{\i0}! When did you--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.27,0:12:22.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.40,0:12:23.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ask!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.90,0:12:27.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Now that we've settled down, we know it was a stupid waste of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.34,0:12:29.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't hurt us any more!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.91,0:12:29.34,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(361,42)}"Duel!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.81,0:12:33.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you gals couldn't pull this off by yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.01,0:12:35.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ya didn't even clean the place up one bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.25,0:12:37.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Whoops!\N--Don't give me "whoops!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.49,0:12:39.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you come, Hiro-{\i1}nii{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.49,0:12:44.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's only gonna get colder, so I figured I'd set the window slides up for the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.36,0:12:47.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, Sensei's place ain't got them window slides.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.43,0:12:52.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The glass broke in the hurricane, so I took 'em off and stored 'em at my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.03,0:12:55.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll give the instructions, so you go and get the place cleaned up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.87,0:12:57.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Aww...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.17,0:13:00.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei's gonna be back, so we better hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.11,0:13:01.51,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(361,45)}"(keep) flammable" "(discard) nonflammable"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.44,0:13:01.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Separate the trash!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.84,0:13:03.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta! Use the broom and sweep the place clean!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.11,0:13:04.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.11,0:13:06.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You two wipe 'em clean!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.15,0:13:08.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's a lot cleaner than before, Hiro-{\i1}nii.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.32,0:13:11.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You gals clean too! Don't leave a single speck!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.49,0:13:14.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, relax a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.12,0:13:16.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is for Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.19,0:13:18.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,For Sensei. For Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.83,0:13:21.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--For Sensei!\N--For Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.83,0:13:23.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,For Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.30,0:13:25.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,For Sensei...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.03,0:13:27.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,For Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.34,0:13:30.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Clean up...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.57,0:13:32.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.07,0:13:34.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So clean!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.24,0:13:37.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Now we can dirty the place up all we want!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.55,0:13:40.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That almost sounds like you'd do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.05,0:13:42.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,All we gotta do is wait for\NSensei to come back now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.72,0:13:44.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.35,0:13:45.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Neither can Naru!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.35,0:13:48.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go home and bring back some snacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.42,0:13:50.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hiro-{\i1}nii{\i0}, can you go and cook something for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.22,0:13:53.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You serious about dirtying up the place again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.27,0:14:01.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.54,0:14:09.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Village Leader was supposed to pick me up, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.35,0:14:14.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If I start walking, I'm sure I'll see him shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.45,0:14:23.39,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,42)}"Evaluation Room"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.55,0:14:23.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Seishu-{\i1}kun{\i0}'s calligraphy should be up shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.79,0:14:27.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I haven't seen it, so I'm looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.90,0:14:30.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kanzaki-{\i1}kun{\i0}'s calligraphy was wonderful too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.73,0:14:34.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like it's going to be a duel between those two young ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.24,0:14:40.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I only wish that my son sees not just the results, but what lies beyond them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.98,0:14:45.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I believe Seishu-{\i1}kun{\i0} is acting with a clear vision towards the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.78,0:14:48.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,He's experienced more than his fair share of pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.12,0:14:52.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure his impulsive actions will fade away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.39,0:14:56.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,His impulsive actions will fade away...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.96,0:14:58.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I can only hope so...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.83,0:15:04.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Village Leader... Not yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.90,0:15:06.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,A vending machine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.77,0:15:08.74,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(361,45)}"impulsive"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.30,0:15:12.17,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(361,45)}"pain"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.11,0:15:14.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry... My wallet...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.51,0:15:16.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wha--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.18,0:15:18.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Money...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.08,0:15:18.78,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(361,45)}"pain"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.91,0:15:21.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Money... Money... Tea... Tea...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.65,0:15:24.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.45,0:15:26.64,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,45)}"Hot-n-Lumpy Corn"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.45,0:15:26.64,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(361,73)}"warm"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.12,0:15:26.64,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(361,107)}"pain"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.15,0:15:30.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it too early to stock winter drinks...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.16,0:15:36.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.16,0:15:40.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Sensei! Whatcha doin' 'round here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.20,0:15:42.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Did you come to pick me up by any chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.47,0:15:45.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Nah! Just takin' a drive!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.14,0:15:47.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Village Leader?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.64,0:15:49.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.48,0:15:51.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna hitch a ride?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.29,0:16:03.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, this is just like when I first came.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.89,0:16:05.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.87,0:16:16.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The weather today is beautiful, so it looks gorgeous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.24,0:16:22.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothin' special. 'Bout like normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.01,0:16:23.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Normal...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.51,0:16:28.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Normal... is the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.32,0:16:32.22,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(361,45)}"A call from Kawafuji-{\i1}san{\i0} came in"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.19,0:16:37.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hello! Kinoshita Shoten.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.56,0:16:39.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Kawafuji-{\i1}san.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.03,0:16:41.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I believe Sensei is back already.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.93,0:16:44.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Village Leader went to...\N--Sensei, 'round here okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.87,0:16:46.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?! I can't hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.67,0:16:48.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--'Round here okay?!\N--Please wait a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.74,0:16:49.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Huh?!\N--Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.87,0:16:51.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.85,0:17:02.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,When Sensei opens the door, we're gonna pop these!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.28,0:17:03.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Naru's gonna tackle him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.95,0:17:05.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! You do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.02,0:17:09.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Here already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.92,0:17:11.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's just you, Aki.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.53,0:17:13.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.06,0:17:14.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.60,0:17:17.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,He's on the phone with\NKawafuji-{\i1}san{\i0} at the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.63,0:17:19.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like the exhibit results are finalized.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.77,0:17:21.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? That's quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.60,0:17:22.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.77,0:17:26.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Right... If it's second place, he'll be down again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.41,0:17:29.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, Sensei's an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.74,0:17:31.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,He won't say anything that'll make things worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.75,0:17:33.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Are you kidding, Hiro-{\i1}nii{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.05,0:17:35.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate\NSensei's childlike behavior!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.58,0:17:38.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mess with the feelin' of getting second place!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.62,0:17:40.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei's back, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.62,0:17:42.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--What?!\N--Huh? Where's my popper?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.82,0:17:44.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You had it with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.46,0:17:46.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Where's mine?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.63,0:17:48.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Who got mine?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.33,0:17:51.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Found 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.67,0:17:53.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.68,0:18:06.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't funny...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.45,0:18:07.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.95,0:18:09.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.32,0:18:12.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,After being away this long, this is what I get?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.95,0:18:14.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.12,0:18:16.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Your hands... are kind of sticky...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.76,0:18:18.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like he's in a good mood...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.49,0:18:20.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Should be okay, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.76,0:18:22.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.03,0:18:24.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,How was the calligraphy contest?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.97,0:18:27.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Did ya get first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.27,0:18:28.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Naru?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.27,0:18:30.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I told ya not to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.37,0:18:32.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This is a delicate issue, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.31,0:18:33.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ya don't say...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.31,0:18:36.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei? Don't worry 'bout what she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.04,0:18:39.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Are you girls... worried about the exhibit results?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.88,0:18:42.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Ya got good results?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.35,0:18:45.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.72,0:18:47.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Yay!\N--Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.12,0:18:49.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--I'm so happy!\N--Good for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.56,0:18:55.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, cheer up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.46,0:18:58.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The elder group was too good this time around.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.50,0:19:03.04,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,42)}"Results
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.50,0:19:03.04,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,75)}5th Handa Sei (Seishu)
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.50,0:19:03.04,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,104)}7th Kanzaki Kosuke"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.40,0:19:00.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Neither of you were even close to getting an award.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.57,0:19:03.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Bet they didn't want any youngsters having it their way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.54,0:19:06.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But you could say this is how things should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.87,0:19:09.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You came, Kawafuji-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.54,0:19:11.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.18,0:19:13.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You let Seishu know the results?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.58,0:19:17.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it seems like he wanted to know, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.35,0:19:21.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think the results will disappoint him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.05,0:19:23.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well... Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.72,0:19:27.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But that is his first step towards writing his own calligraphy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.90,0:19:30.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be interesting from here on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.93,0:19:33.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.93,0:19:36.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So, what kind of calligraphy did ya write, Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.34,0:19:38.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I want to know too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.04,0:19:40.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The subject isn't that amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.01,0:19:43.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, don't hold back. It was good, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.85,0:19:47.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Not like it's gonna hurt anyone, ya know?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.28,0:19:48.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.68,0:19:50.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If you insist...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.45,0:19:53.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's what I think is most important to me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.45,0:19:58.96,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(361,42)}"Arai Tamako" "Kotoishi Naru"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.45,0:19:58.96,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(361,73)}"Kido Hiroshi" "Yamamura Miwa" "Kubota Hina"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.72,0:19:55.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Important to you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.09,0:19:59.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Could it be, Hiro-{\i1}nii{\i0}...?!\N--Must be the calligraphy we wrote!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.96,0:20:03.70,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(361,42)}"Kotoishi Naru"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.09,0:20:00.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.86,0:20:03.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You girls are so shallow.\NPeople are what they eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.70,0:20:07.27,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(361,42)}"Kido Hiroshi" "Yamamura Miwa" "Kubota Hina"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.96,0:20:05.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing to do with food.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.60,0:20:08.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Then... maybe a rabbit?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.30,0:20:09.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about, Hina?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.64,0:20:11.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was a beetle!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.47,0:20:12.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I thought a praying mantis!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.97,0:20:14.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Then I say a scorpion!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.37,0:20:16.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, stop bothering Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.98,0:20:19.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Aki, you're acting like a pet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.21,0:20:20.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.78,0:20:23.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're actin' too cool, Aki.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.32,0:20:24.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.82,0:20:26.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.92,0:20:30.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.16,0:20:32.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...it's always fun bein' with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.57,0:20:45.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Looking at you kids having fun freely is... influencing me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.24,0:20:46.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Influencing...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.28,0:20:54.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It just means this time now is what's important.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.31,0:20:56.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.58,0:20:59.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.19,0:21:10.93,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(361,45)}"Happy Yer Home"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.70,0:21:10.93,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,76)}"By Naru"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.02,0:22:50.96,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(361,45)}"Happy Yer Home"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.02,0:22:50.96,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(361,76)}"Illustration by Tachibana Masaki"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.56,0:22:43.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ready...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.02,0:22:46.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.76,0:22:49.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
